ica, arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;color:#333333;font-size:16px">The c=
atch, and the reason the forecast looks credible rather than hopeful, is th=
at demand is outrunning supply. Lumentum says it is short-shipping customer=
s by around 30% because it cannot make these laser chips fast enough, and N=
vidia signed a multi-year partnership with the company earlier this year.</=
